-----------Deadline Extension & Final Call for Papers------------

Due to several requests, the deadline for regular paper 
submissions has been extended to 11th of February 2008, 11pm (GMT)
Please note that this is a strict deadline.

In order to correspond to some authors' wishes, please also note
that submission of papers for a blind review process, i.e., no 
disclosure of names and affiliations on the paper, are also 
accepted. In addition, our reviewing system supports consideration
of conflicts of interest.

